sequenceDiagram
    participant CICD as CI/CD Pipeline<br/>(GitHub Actions / Konflux)
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>(Go CLI)
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant Quay as quay.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Container as Data Container<br/>UBI9-minimal
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard

    Note over CICD,Quay: Flow 1: Build-Time Catalog Generation

    CICD->>Extractor: Execute model-extractor

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Extractor,HF: Step 1: Model Discovery
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/users/RedHatAI/collections<br/>TLS 1.2+ | No Auth (public)
        HF-->>Extractor: Validated model collections
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/collections/{id}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | No Auth
        HF-->>Extractor: Collection details with model IDs
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Extractor,Registry: Step 2: OCI Image Inspection
        Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{image}/manifests/{tag}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Docker auth (config.json)
        Registry-->>Extractor: OCI manifest (layers list)
        Extractor->>Registry: GET /v2/{image}/blobs/{digest}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Docker auth
        Registry-->>Extractor: Layer blob (modelcard.md)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Extractor,HF: Step 3: Metadata Enrichment
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/models/{id}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | No Auth
        HF-->>Extractor: Model details (tags, license, downloads)
        Extractor->>HF: GET /{model}/raw/main/README.md<br/>TLS 1.2+ | No Auth
        HF-->>Extractor: README (YAML frontmatter)
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over Extractor,FS: Step 4: Catalog Generation
        Extractor->>FS: Parse modelcard.md + enrichment data
        Extractor->>FS: Merge dynamic + static models
        Extractor->>FS: Deduplicate entries
        Extractor->>FS: Write models-catalog.yaml
        Extractor->>FS: Write validated-models-catalog.yaml
    end

    CICD->>Quay: docker push data container image<br/>HTTPS/443 | Registry credentials
    Quay-->>CICD: Image pushed successfully

    Note over Container,Dashboard: Flow 2: Runtime Catalog Delivery

    Container->>Container: sleep infinity (no network activity)
    Dashboard->>Container: Volume mount /app/data
    Container-->>Dashboard: models-catalog.yaml<br/>validated-models-catalog.yaml
